sequenceDiagram
    participant OC as OAuth Client
    participant MW as Client Auth Middleware
    participant TE as Thunder /oauth2/token

    OC->>MW: POST /oauth2/token<br/>grant_type=refresh_token&refresh_token=...<br/>+ Client Auth
    MW->>MW: Validate client credentials
    MW->>TE: Forward authenticated request
    TE->>TE: Validate & decode refresh_token JWT
    TE->>TE: Verify client_id match
    TE->>TE: Intersect requested scopes with original scopes
    TE->>TE: Build new access_token (JWT/RS256)
    TE->>TE: Optionally rotate refresh_token (renew_on_grant)
    TE->>OC: Token Response {access_token, refresh_token (if rotated)}
